items.htmlTitle: Approximate max-flow min-cut theorem - Wikipedia, the free ...
items.snippet:
According to the famous Ford–Fulkerson algorithm (see Ford–Fulkerson 
algorithm),the max-flow and min-cut are always equal in a 1-commodity flow 
problem.
